{"tid":416863,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[箍牙年經]求箍骨釘的牙醫推介","createTime":"2017-09-28T06:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T02:18:37.000Z","uid":34978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7561daac59a75111004932d56a5ee4a89a7a12","tid":416863,"uid":34978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:42:05.000Z","msg":"想箍牙好多年了<br />\n我啲牙算齊嘅但係少少哨，同埋嘴突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個口放鬆哂時會有少少合唔埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇過下，我諗我係骨性哨牙（冇照過x-ray冇做過consultation，自己估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n聽講普通箍牙對骨性哨牙改善不大，要落骨釘先得<br />\n想問有冇箍過骨釘嘅巴絲有牙醫推介？價錢地點都冇所謂<br />\n唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b6b641d5a3db2af5976c97c63379d1c6fc9f18","tid":416863,"uid":75385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:17:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想箍牙好多年了<br />\n我啲牙算齊嘅但係少少哨，同埋嘴突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個口放鬆哂時會有少少合唔埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇過下，我諗我係骨性哨牙（冇照過x-ray冇做過consultation，自己估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n聽講普通箍牙對骨性哨牙改善不大，要落骨釘先得<br />\n想問有冇箍過骨釘嘅巴絲有牙醫推介？價錢地點都冇所謂<br />\n唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如搵間專科望下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係骨釘應該得佢地有<br />\n但其實嘴凸好難靠箍牙改善 個個都俾ab呃哂<br />\n有時問題可能係下巴到 根本要整容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申釘土姑娘 自己都嘴凸做佐少少research"},{"pid":"a723159fc4dadb64ee9c2472743e348793d8eb9d","tid":416863,"uid":34978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T10:25:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想箍牙好多年了<br />\